    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hand-held implements having a long shaft mounted with a curved metal head with a sharpened point at one end and an adze-like blade at the other; for similar implements, but lacking the adze-like blade, use "pick-axes."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
